  <FAQs
    title="DFY Pricing FAQs"
    subtitle="Choosing the right plan is important. Here are the answers to our most common pricing questions."
    columns={1}
    items={[
      {
        title: 'What does "DFY" mean in the One-Time Bundles?',
        description:
          'DFY stands for "Done-For-You." It means our expert team handles the entire setup process from start to finish, including design, development, integration, and initial configuration. You only provide the vision and key content.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Are there any recurring costs with the One-Time Bundles?',
        description:
          'The price listed is a one-time fee for the setup and delivery of the service. You will be responsible for standard third-party software costs (like hosting, CRM, or chatbot license fees, if applicable) after the setup is complete. We ensure you own all accounts.',
      },
      {
        title: 'How is the Monthly Retainer different from the One-Time Bundle?',
        description:
          'The **One-Time Bundle** is for building a new system (e.g., a website or an AI agent). The **Monthly Retainer** is for ongoing maintenance, optimization, and growth activities (like SEO content, technical fixes, and performance tuning) on the systems we have built or you already own.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Can I combine a One-Time Bundle with a Monthly Retainer?',
        description:
          'Yes, this is highly recommended! Starting with a One-Time Bundle ensures a perfect setup, and following up with a Monthly Retainer ensures the asset is maintained, secured, and optimized for continuous growth.',
      },
      {
        title: 'What happens if I need more features than a plan offers?',
        description:
          'We can always customize a plan for you! Simply book a strategy session, and we will create a bespoke bundle that includes the specific high-end features and services you require.',
      },
    ]}
  />

